(9438, 713, '_story_button_2_url', 'field_5d7225f86965e'),
(9439, 713, 'more_story_content', '<p class=\"text-center text-white\">Our story begins in a 16 station outpatient dialysis facility, Center for Renal Replacement, where an externship program was established to assist the community’s post-graduate dialysis technologist students in obtaining the required clinical hours that would qualify them to sit for their certification exam (BONENT).</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-center mt-3 text-white\">After many years of encountering post-graduates who required extensive re-training of basic skills and knowledge of materials that should have been mastered upon graduation of an approved dialysis technologist program the decision to improve the educational process began to shape and grow.</p>'),
