(14444, 825, 'our_vision_content', '&nbsp;\r\n<p class=\"gmail-text-center gmail-mt-5\" style=\"text-align: center;\">To provide a quality education that will empower students with the knowledge, technical skills, and professional experience. Delmon Medical College will be the driving force behind a student’s success.</p>\r\n<p class=\"gmail-text-center gmail-mt-3\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Our mission is to offer exemplary post-secondary career training programs which provide students with comprehensive knowledge, technical expertise, and values necessary to attain their educational and professional goals.</p>'),
