(14456, 826, 'tuition_content', '<p class=\"text-center mt-5 \">Delmon Medical College manages the Dr. James K. Yeung Scholarship Fund. The James K. Yeung, M.D. Scholarship is available to applicants based on their academic placement test (taken upon enrollment). Qualified students enrolling in DMC’s Dialysis Technologist Training Program (DTTP) and Medical Assistant Diploma Training Program (MADTP) are eligible to receive a merit scholarship of $2,500. This scholarship does not apply to students enrolled in other programs: Basic Nursing Assistant Training Program (BNATP)</p>'),
