(14544, 829, 'story_content', '<p class=\"text-center mt-5\">Delmon Medical College is not just a classroom. It is as effective as on the job training, as it has a fully operational dialysis facility to educate students in a real-life medical environment. This unique experience is only available at Delmon Medical College. The dialysis facility on-site is Center for Renal Replacement (CRR), an independent, family-owned 16 station chronic outpatient dialysis facility.</p>'),
