(14672, 831, 'scholarship_content', '<p class=\"text-center mt-5 \">The James K. Yeung, M.D. Scholarship* is available to applicants based on their academic placement test (taken upon enrollment). DT and MA qualifying students enrolling in DMC programs are eligible to receive a merit scholarship of <strong>$2,500.</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"text-center mt-3 \">*Must meet merit-based qualifications and enrollment-based criteria. Scholarships are subject to approval and availability of funds. Specific eligibility criteria apply. Scholarships will be awarded as $2500 towards tuition. This scholarship cannot be used in combination with any other offer, award or group-specific tuition rate.</p>\r\n<p class=\"text-center mt-5 \"><strong>For more information contact Maria Lupascu. mlupascu@delmonmedicalcollege.com</strong></p>'),
