(634, 1, '2019-09-06 11:02:23', '2019-09-06 11:02:23', 'Ted Simmons brings to Delmon Medical College his project management skills and technical expertise. An entrepreneur, Mr. Simmons has been involved with many start-up businesses. In 1989, he founded Floors of Distinction, Ltd., a custom flooring company. With works displayed at the Merchandise Mart, Chicago, he collaborated with many interior design firms and had installation pieces featured at major retailers and residences both here and abroad. Mr. Simmons received a BA in Visual Communications from the Illinois Institute of Art, Chicago in 2000.', 'Ted Simmons', 'CEO & CO-FOUNDER OF DELMON MEDICAL COLLEGE', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ted-simmons', '', '', '2019-10-08 18:09:06', '2019-10-08 18:09:06', '', 0, 'https://delmonmedicalcollege.com/?post_type=trustees&#038;p=634', 0, 'trustees', '', 0),
(635, 1, '2019-09-06 11:03:28', '2019-09-06 11:03:28', 'As most nurses do upon graduation, Rick DelValle entered the field that would allow him to immediately put the newly acquired skills to work, that was in Telemetry at McNeal Hospital. Being involved with patients who have critical cardiac morbidities and responsible for providing life sustaining medical interventions provided great personal satisfaction. His perception of being an asset to his community and having an effect on patients’ lives flourished.', 'Richard Delvalle, BA, RN, CNN', 'PRESIDENT', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'richard-delvalle-ba-rn-cnn', '', '', '2019-10-08 18:08:35', '2019-10-08 18:08:35', '', 0, 'https://delmonmedicalcollege.com/?post_type=trustees&#038;p=635', 0, 'trustees', '', 0),
(636, 1, '2019-09-06 11:04:39', '2019-09-06 11:04:39', 'In 2010 Maria Lupascu began her career in higher education as an adjunct instructor at Sanford Brown College. In 2013 while program director and a member of the faculty, she took on a new challenge. Maria engaged in developing a new program of study as part of the Midwestern Career College academic team. 2018 was another watershed year when she accepted the Vice Presidency of Academic Affairs at Delmon Medical College.', 'Maria Lupascu, CHT, BBA, MEd', 'VICE PRESIDENT OF ACADEMIC AFFAIRS', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'maria-lupascu-cht-bba-med', '', '', '2019-10-08 17:18:47', '2019-10-08 17:18:47', '', 0, 'https://delmonmedicalcollege.com/?post_type=trustees&#038;p=636', 0, 'trustees', '', 0),
